post_data: Yesterday I decided I was giving up on writing. I am the worst writer ever. Why am I even doing this? No one even cares. This is stupid. So dumb. title: "Why the hell did you
post_data: "Why the hell did you decide to change? You had mastered the art of not changing. You could have just stuck with that. But, while no change means you won’t have to do the work of changing, it also means this: You won’t ever know what the changed you looks like. And, oh my goodness, what if she’s fantastic?" <3 New post on the blog (link in comments below).
